{"tid":1924550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候捐錢俾意大利賑災","createTime":"2020-03-13T17:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T23:56:29.000Z","uid":70786,"like":43,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8afad4d4b5acdc05c045937f7f7e14cd4905ee30","tid":1924550,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"因為武漢肺炎死咗成１２６６人<br />\n隔籬個post有巴打個意大利朋友一家七口死剩佢同細佬<br />\n而佢自己情況都唔樂觀<br />\n短短一段時間就家破人亡變孤兒<br />\n我地香港人不如搞個籌款<br />\n表明我地stand with Italy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知實會有人屌佢地一帶一路奶共<br />\n但係意大利國會係表態過反送中<br />\n係手足嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛唔撚使旨意分化<br />\n幫支那口交部叫春叫爽譴責埋我地係別有用心<br />\n我地擺到明就係唔捐俾支那<br />\n支那賤畜仆街死全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6d37751d2b5339b1d1babd424b4b493ac2bbef","tid":1924550,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c60e83486d1dce292dfea6880142353765ffd1","tid":1924550,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:54:35.000Z","msg":"中國真係累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c59f656a575db2f56826f600387362fd848141","tid":1924550,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab76e36bebda6b23ce29b13b2171bc4af009bca","tid":1924550,"uid":2584,"like":2,"disl